Distribution.
The species is distributed in the northeastern Atlantic and the Mediterranean: Southern North Sea, Eastern Atlantic (
Ireland
, English Channel) to the coast of 
Guinea
(
Ngoc-Ho, 2003
); the entire Mediterranean including Tyrrhenean, Aegean, Ionian, Adriatic basins (
Petagna, 1792
; Saint Laurent & Bozic 1976; 
Števčić, 1990
; de Vaugelas, 1991, 1998; 
Dworschak, 1992
; 
Ngoc-Ho, 2003
; 
Sakai, 2011
); intertidal and shallow subtidal zones down to 
20 m
or deeper (
Dworschak, 1998
), burrowing in fine sand or muddy sand with or without seagrass (d’Udekem d’Acoz, 1986; 
Števčić, 1990
; 
Dworschak, 1992
). The occurrence of the species in the 
Black Sea
is re- ported for the first time.
